songs.title: Nymph
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus: Chløë Black & Brooke Candy]
When I was a little girl
All I needed was love (Wow)
Now I am a big girl (Yeah)
All I need is love, love, love, love, love
Brooke Candy

[Verse 1: Brooke Candy]
Girls, they call me lil' quim fort
Tongue so good, I'm sinful
You could have my info, 1-800-NYMPHO
Click, click, clicking on that clit, clit
Feeling feeling lit, lit
When you hear that brrr, click, click
Manic Pixie Dream Girl with the baby pink pearl
Lips like sugar fish, splashing 'em like SeaWorld
Click, click, clicking on that clit, clit
Feeling, feeling lit, lit
When you hear that, brrr, click, click

[Chorus: Chløë Black & Brooke Candy]
When I was a little girl (Wow)
All I needed was love (Wow)
Now I am a big girl (Yeah)
All I need is love, love, love, love, love (Brooke Candy)

[Verse 2: Brooke Candy]
Tinkerbell, tinker-hell, ménage me like a carousel
Juicy ass, DSL, I'll make you wet like Ariel
Click, click, clicking on that clit, clit
Feeling feeling lit, lit
When you hear that brrr, click, click
I'm suckin' my unicorn every night
My fairies and sirens be swimming in Sprite
Cannibalize you like Lord of the Flies
Face of an angel with dark appetites
Click, click, clicking on that clit, clit
Feeling feeling lit, lit
When you hear that brrr, click, click
Fine, golly, it's the land of milk and honey
I'm the Energizer bunny, know I'm stacked like Peg Bundy

[Outro: Brooke Candy]
I feel like, I feel like, I feel like a (Uh) nymph
I feel like, I feel like, I feel like a (Uh) nymph
I feel like, I feel like, I feel like a (Uh) nymph
I feel like, I feel like, I feel like a (Uh) nymph
